season.info:
A *season* is the span of time, of usually 6 months where players compete for the top 10 slots on the money or reputation leaderboard. The winners will get badges and prizes based on their seasonal performance.
This is to allow a more competitive frame (before, money was pretty much stale) and to make the game a bit more fun.
You can access seasonal stuff using `-season`. Commands like profile, mine, fish and balance will require it, while games, loot, daily and reputation will give money/rep to both your global and seasonal profile.
season.info_2:
The current season is **%1$s** and **%2$s** players are currently taking part on it!

The fun begins, check `~>leaderboard money -season`; `~>leaderboard rep -season` and `~>leaderboard games -season`.
Game on! <3
Thanks for enjoying Mantaro.

ls.description:
**This shows all of the custom (user-made) commands of this server.** Every command here is not associated with the bot itself in any shape or form.

Custom commands are commands created by users (usually server admins) which can handle a bunch of different situations, going as far as emulating action commands.
For more information on how to make custom commands refer to [this wiki page.](https://github.com/Mantaro/MantaroBot/wiki/Custom-Commands)

pet.explanation:
Peliharaan adalah rekan yang berguna dalam mencari uang!
Mereka bisa membantumu dapat uang lebih, dapat jarahan lebih, menemukan barang di tambang, menebang pohon, dan bahkan menangkap ikan. Semakin tinggi levelnya, semakin tinggi hadiahnya!
Memilih peliharaan yang tepat untuk aktivitasmu itu penting, jadi pastikan untuk memeriksa jenis dan kemampuan peliharaan yang ingin kamu pilih!
Ingatlah bahwa peliharaan perlu diberi makan dan minum, serta sesekali beristirahat untuk mengisi energinya, seperti peliharaan sungguhan! Kamu juga bisa mengelus-elusnya :)
Ada dua jenis: Pribadi (untuk diri sendiri) dan Pernikahan (dibagi antara kamu dan pasanganmu). Pilih dengan `~> pet choice`. Defaultnya adalah Pribadi.
Untuk bantuan lebih lanjut, gunakan `~> help pet` dan` ~> pet list` untuk lihat daftar hewan peliharaan.

birthday_enable.no_args: %1$sYou need to specify the channel name and the role name.
birthday_enable.public_role: %1$sYou cannot set the everyone role as a birthday role! Remember that the birthday role is a role that gets assigned to the person when the birthday comes, and then removes when the day passes away.
birthday_enable.autorole: %1$sYou cannot set the autorole role as a birthday role! Remember that the birthday role is a role that gets assigned to the person when the birthday comes, and then removes when the day passes away.
birthday_enable.warning: %1$sRemember that the birthday role is a role that gets assigned to the person when the birthday comes, and then removes when the day passes away.If you have any doubts on how to configure it, you can always join our support guild and ask. You can also check `~>opts help birthday enable` for an example.
birthday_enable.warning_1: This is because of how the birthday assigner works: It assigns a temporary role to the person having its birthday, and un-assigns it when the birthday day has passed. **This means that everyone with the birthday role will get the role removed the day the birthday passes through**. Please take caution when choosing what role to use, as a misconfiguration might make bad things happen (really)!
birthday_enable.warning_2: The role *has to be a newly created role or a role you don't use for anyone else*. It MUST NOT be a role you already have on your users. Users will need to allow this server to announce their birthday by using `~>birthday allowserver` else their birthday won't appear! Read <https://github.com/Mantaro/MantaroBot/wiki/Changes-to-the-birthday-announcement-system> for more info.
birthday_enable.warning_3: Additionally the birthday cache (what is used to store them) is only updated every 23 hours. Meaning if you set your birthday today to tomorrow to test this announcer it will **not** work.
birthday_enable.warning_4: Type **yes** if you agree to set the role %2$s as a birthday role, and **no** to cancel. This timeouts in 45 seconds.

explanation.pick: A normal pickaxe you bought on the local market. Seems sturdy enough to mine some stuff.
explanation.diamond_pick: A diamond pick is definitely stronger than the market-bought iron picks I could get on the market, that's for sure!
explanation.comet_pick:
Kamu menemukan beberapa Comet Fragment dan sadar bisa membuat Comet Gem darinya.
Benda apa itu? Apakah itu istimewa?
Kamu begitu ingin mencobanya setelah terkesan dengan cahayanya, dan ini adalah langkah pertamamu dalam mendapatkan belencong yang lebih kuat.
explanation.star_pick:
Maybe it was the glow, maybe it was the fact they came from a star far away in the galaxy, but it seemed to make for quite a sturdy pick with special properties.
Weird... it seems to attract more gems. Is it the effect of the material, or is it my skill getting better?
explanation.moon_pick:
Benda yang mirip bulan ini membuatmu kagum.
Apa karena pancarannya seperti bulan purnama, atau karena bisa melayang?
Bagaimanapun juga, kamu mencoba menyatukannya dengan belencongmu, dan hasilnya cukup memuaskan.
Seimbang akan gelap dan terang, dan entah bagaimana aku bisa menambang sejumlah permata dengan ini.
Apa pecahan ini berasal dari bulan yang jauh?
explanation.sparkle_pick:
Saat kamu mendongak ke atas gua, kamu menemukan permata yang berkilauan. Saat itu juga, beberapa pecahannya jatuh ke belencongmu dan membuatnya bercahaya, cukup untuk menyinari gua.
Tanpa pikir panjang, kamu mengambil beberapa pecahan berkilauan itu dan pergi ke tempat mencetak.
Belencongnya silau seperti cahaya matahari... dan lumayan kokoh juga... bagaimana caranya bisa menyatu dengan besi?
explanation.hellfire_pick:
Reactions between all the elements can be a weird and dangerous process.
Regardless of what your friends told you, you decided to research this topic, and came up with an object brighter than anything you've ever seen...
It seems to be a mix of all the other elements, but it seems quite reactive... it's also quite tough, not much seems to be able to break it...
Have I done good for this world, or have I brought the unknown to life?
explanation.axe: A normal axe you bought on the local market. Good enough to chop some trees down.
explanation.comet_axe: After testing the Comet Fragments on your pick, you also realized you could use them on your axe. It made it stronger, and shinier. All you could wish for.
explanation.star_axe:
A bright glow from a star far away, but in your hands.
Looks like the tree-chopping can continue with this new, shiny axe. You seemed weirded out at first: how can this help me mine more wood?
Well, you soon realized why...
explanation.sparkle_axe:
A touch of sparkle here, a touch of sparkle there!
The axe glows bright like the sun... and it seems pretty tough too... how did it fuse so well with iron?
explanation.moon_axe:
Looking at this axe, you look mesmerized by moon-like glow it emits.
Was it the fact it glowed like a full moon, or was it the fact it seemed to float on its own?
Mesmerized, you cast this substance into your axe and... boom!
The results look good. It seems to chop trees faster, too. Why is it so sharp? Is this really a fragment from a far away moon?
explanation.hellfire_axe:
Reactions between all the elements can be a weird and dangerous process.
You mastered the elements already, and fusing it with your axe now seemed trivial. Maybe it was the glow, maybe it was the fire, but you had to do it.
It works wonders. Nothing can compare. But you're still left wondering whether you really did the right thing.
explanation.rod: A rod you bought at your local fishing market. Looks sturdy.
explanation.comet_rod: After testing the Comet Fragments on your axe, you also realized you could use them on your rod. It made the thread stronger, and it seemed to attract more fish to it. All you could wish for.
explanation.star_rod: The mesmerizing and shiny glow of this fragment could not be overlooked. You fused it together with the thread of your rod, and the fish came flowing through it! Seems like a bait isn't necessary all the time, but it's still useful.
explanation.moon_rod:
Kamu masih kagum dengan cara permatanya mengambang. Meski begitu, kamu tetap mencampurnya dengan benang pancingmu sebisanya. Sepertinya ini sedikit lebih kokoh dari pancing yang diisi Star Fragment.
Bagaimanapun juga, kamu menikmati pancarannya seakan baru pertama melihatnya.
explanation.sparkle_rod:
Berkilauan sekali!
Kamu melumat Sparkle Fragments dan melapisi benang pancingmu dengan itu.
Kamu kebingungan. Kok ini bisa dipakai mancing ikan, ya?
Dunia penuh dengan misteri, dan ini salah satunya. Mungkin ini bisa membantumu dapat kredit lebih. Mungkin juga bisa membuatmu puas.
Cahaya yang memantul saat dipakai memancing sangatlah indah, dan kau menatapnya selama berjam-jam. Anggap saja tindakanmu ini sudah benar.
explanation.hellfire_rod:
Reactions between all the elements can be a weird and dangerous process.
You mastered the elements already, and fusing it with your fishing rod thread now seemed trivial. Maybe it was the glow, maybe it was the fire, but you had to do it.
It works wonders. Fish come in shoals to you. Nothing can compare. But you're still left wondering whether you really did the right thing.
explanation.wrench: Kunci pas biasa yang bisa dibeli dari pasar. Berguna untuk memperbaiki barang.
explanation.comet_wrench: Kunci pas yang diisi dengan potongan Comet Gems. Terasa lebih kokoh.
explanation.sparkle_wrench: Kunci pas yang diisi dengan cuilan Sparkle Fragments. Terasa jauh lebih kokoh.

description.tuxedo: Setelan yang kamu pakai saat mau menikah dengan perempuan, atau mau pergi ke tempat yang mewah, atau kemana saja, siapa yang tahu?
description.shoes: Karena bertelanjang kaki itu menjijikkan. Atau menyakitkan.
description.rose: Perwujudan cintamu. Bagus juga buat dekorasi.
description.die_2: Even more loaded. `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.booster: Used to give you some kind of boost, now it's broken. `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.berserk: Currency Berserk? Anyone? `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.companion: Aw, such a cute dog. `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.special_ring: It's so special, it's not even a ring. `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.enchancer: A broken enchanter, I wonder if it could be fixed? `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.prize: Pretty much, huh? `Leftover from Currency version 1. No longer obtainable.`
description.crate: You can use this along with a loot key to open a loot crate! Can be opened with `~>opencrate`
description.prize_2: In the first place, how did you get so much money?
description.slot_ticket: Memberimu peluang ekstra di slots, dan berfungsi juga sebagai penyimpanan massal.
description.bell: Christmas reward. Gives you a cozy christmas feeling on your tree.
description.tree: Christmas reward. Who doesn't like a christmas tree?.
description.pants: Yang selalu kamu pakai di kaki... Semoga saja pakai.
description.haste: Allows you to collect more stuff from currency commands for 3 commands.
description.energy: Makes a tool lose less durability per swing. Lasts 3 commands.
description.rod: A basic rod for your fishing activities.
description.blowfish: Rasanya... enak tidak ya? Didapat dari memancing.
description.comet_gem: Cuilan komet yang kamu temukan saat menambang. Berguna untuk pencetakan.
description.star_gem: Cuilan dari bintang jatuh yang kamu temukan saat menambang.
description.cobweb: Benda yang ditinggalkan laba-laba di tambang. Entah harganya berapa.
description.fragment: Pecahan dari permata kuno. Berguna untuk pencetakan.
description.mop: Cara mudah untuk membersihkan debu-debu di sekitarmu. Pasti banyak debunya.
description.claim_key: This item makes you un-claimeable (as a waifu) when you run `~>profile claimlock`
description.waifu_pill: Gives you a significant advantage on mine and fish if one of your waifus is valued at over 20,000. Lasts 3 sessions.
description.bait: Gives you a higher chance of catching fish.
description.star_wrench: Alat mencetak. Berguna untuk membuat item. Peluang rusak lebih kecil, penting untuk membuat beberapa item sekaligus. Tingkat 3.
description.sparkle_wrench: Alat mencetak. Berguna untuk membuat item. Peluang rusak lebih kecil. Biaya tiap pembuatan lebih murah. Tingkat 4.
description.motorcycle: Berpindah tempat, pakai cara yang keren.
description.sparkle: Salah satu permata terlangka yang ada. Simpan baik-baik. Bisa dipakai buat membuat Sparkle Pickaxe & Sparkle Rod.
description.sparkle_pick: One of the strongests pick out there.

description.fish_crate: Harta Karun yang kamu temukan saat memancing mungkin punya item bagus di dalamnya. Bisa dibuka dengan `~>opencrate treasure`

description.shell: Ditemukan di dasar laut. Kira-kira berapa harganya?
description.moon: Moon Rune. Dibutuhkan untuk membuat sejumlah item.
description.flake: Snowflake. Biasanya dipakai untuk bahan mencetak.

description.broken_sparkle_pick: A sparkle pick that broke while mining. Still salvageable.

description.broken_sparkle_rod: A sparkle rod that broke while fishing. Still salvageable.

description.incubator_egg: Salah satu bahan yang kamu butuhkan untuk memulangkan peliharaan pribadimu.
description.water_bottle: An item that magically heals your pet's thirst.
description.magic_watch: A magic watch that slows time when you need it. This will automatically be consumed to save your daily streak!
description.pet_house: Rumah untuk hewan peliharaanmu. Kadang. Soalnya mereka juga suka tidur di luar.
description.steak: Very yummy if you're not vegetarian.
description.chicken: Very yummy if you're not vegetarian, but it comes from a chicken instead.
description.milk_3: Very good food for cats, I've heard.
description.dog_food: Food your dog might like a lot. Or they might like bread more, like mines.
description.cat_food: Food your cat might like a lot.
description.wood: Hasil tebang biasa. Berguna untuk pencetakan.
description.leaves: A slow drop from a tree you tried to chop.

description.pear: You happened to chop a pear tree and the pear fell on your head. Ouch.
description.cherry_blossom: A very slow drop from a cherry tree. Lovely, huh?
description.rock: Sebuah batu. Yap. Lumayan keras, ya?
